==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A leading or primary principle, rule, law, or article, which serves as the groundwork of a system; essential part, as, the fundamentals of the Christian faith.

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}

#Pertaining to the foundation or basis; serving for the foundation. Hence: Essential, as an element, principle, or law; important;

